description: These baked veggie samosas are easy to make with pre-made filo pastry and are much healthier than fried.
name: Baked Cauliflower & Spinach Samosas Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Pre-heat the oven to 200°C/180°C fan-forced. Brush the top of the samosas with oil, place on a baking tray and bake for 15 minutes until golden and crisp.
